PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773087075
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in UK as Iran war
OL,4,Centers eighth day
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a second Government charter
OL,7,Fflight carrying British citizens from
OL,8,FOman is expected to land overnight as
OL,9,Fefforts to help people trapped in the
OL,10,Fwar zone continue.
OL,12,FQuestions linger over the UK's future
OL,13,Frole in the conflict, with Foreign
OL,14,FSecretary David Lammy suggesting RAF
OL,15,Fjets could legally strike Iranian
OL,16,Fmissile sites being used to attack
OL,17,FBritish interests in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
