PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773087075
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in UK as Iran war
OL,4,Centers eighth day
OL,6,FAir defence destroyer HMS Dragon is
OL,7,Fnot expected to sail to the eastern
OL,8,FMediterranean until next week while
OL,9,FFrance and Greece have already
OL,10,Fdeployed military assets to defend the
OL,11,Fisland.
OL,13,FOne reason it is taking some time to
OL,14,Fprepare the Type 45 destroyer is
OL,15,Fbecause it is being equipped to remain
OL,16,Fat sea for several months if required,
OL,17,Frather than rushed into the eastern
OL,18,FMediterranean for a short period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
