PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773087075
OL,3,CUS bomber lands in UK as Iran war
OL,4,Centers eighth day
OL,6,FEtihad Airways announced on Friday it
OL,7,Fwould be resuming a "limited
OL,8,Fcommercial flight schedule" until
OL,9,FMarch 19, including flights to and
OL,10,Ffrom Abu Dhabi to Heathrow, Manchester
OL,11,Fand Dublin.
OL,13,FMore than 160,000 people in the region
OL,14,Fhave registered their presence with
OL,15,Fthe Foreign Office as the crisis has
OL,16,Fdeepened.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@[O]
